<div flex-="row gap:1 grow">
  <div flex-="col gap:1" id="sidebar" box-="square">
    <div flex-="row" space-="px:1">
      <button flex-="grow" size-="small">[C] Chat &#xf4ad;</button>
    </div>
    <div flex-="col" space-="px:1" is-="typography-block">
      <div>&#xf4ad; <code>&lt;C-c&gt;</code> New Chat</div>
      <div>&#xf1da; <code>&lt;C-h&gt;</code> History</div>
      <div>&#xf0c7; <code>&lt;C-s&gt;</code> Save Chat</div>
      <div>&#xf1f8; <code>&lt;C-d&gt;</code> Delete Chat</div>
      <hr />
      <div>&#xf085; <code>&lt;C-o&gt;</code> Options</div>
      <div>&#xf2f1; <code>&lt;C-r&gt;</code> Reset Thread</div>
      <div>&#xf05a; <code>&lt;C-i&gt;</code> Information</div>
      <div>&#xf059; <code>&lt;C-q&gt;</code> Help</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div flex-="col grow !basis" box-="square contain:!top" id="chat-container">
    <div flex-="row"><span is-="badge" variant-="background0">AI Assistant</span></div>

    <div flex-="col gap:1" space-="px:1" id="chat-messages">
      <div
        flex-="col gap:1"
        is-="typography-block"
        box-="round contain:none"
        class="message system"
      >
        <div flex-="row justify:between">
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background0"><strong>System</strong></span>
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background0">10:30 AM</span>
        </div>
        <p space-="px:1">
          Welcome to WebTUI Chat! I'm your terminal-based AI assistant. How can I help you today?
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        flex-="col gap:1"
        is-="typography-block"
        box-="round contain:none"
        class="message user"
      >
        <div flex-="row justify:between">
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background0"><strong>User</strong></span>
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background0">10:31 AM</span>
        </div>
        <p space-="px:1">
          Can you tell me about WebTUI and how to use it in my projects?
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        flex-="col gap:1"
        is-="typography-block"
        box-="round contain:none"
        class="message assistant"
      >
        <div flex-="row justify:between">
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background0"><strong>Assistant</strong></span>
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background0">10:31 AM</span>
        </div>
        <p space-="px:1">
          WebTUI is a modular CSS Terminal-like UI library that helps you create terminal-inspired interfaces for the web. Here's how to get started:
        </p>
        <pre space-="px:1">
# Install WebTUI
npm install @webtui/css

# Import in your project
import '@webtui/css';

# Use WebTUI components
&lt;div box-="square"&gt;
  &lt;span is-="badge"&gt;Hello WebTUI!&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
        </pre>
        <p space-="px:1">
          You can also add themes like Nord or Catppuccin for different color schemes. Would you like to see more examples?
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        flex-="col gap:1"
        is-="typography-block"
        box-="round contain:none"
        class="message user"
      >
        <div flex-="row justify:between">
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background0"><strong>User</strong></span>
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background0">10:33 AM</span>
        </div>
        <p space-="px:1">
          Yes, please show me how to create a button with different variants.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        flex-="col gap:1"
        is-="typography-block"
        box-="round contain:none"
        class="message assistant typing"
      >
        <div flex-="row justify:between">
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background0"><strong>Assistant</strong></span>
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background0">10:33 AM</span>
        </div>
        <p space-="px:1" class="typing-indicator">
          <span class="dot">.</span><span class="dot">.</span><span class="dot">.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div flex-="row gap:1" id="chat-input" space-="px:1">
      <input type="text" placeholder="Type your message here..." flex-="grow" />
      <button variant-="background1">&#xf1d8; Send</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div flex-="col grow !basis" box-="square contain:!top" id="info-panel">
    <div flex-="row">
      <span is-="badge" variant-="background0">Information</span>
    </div>

    <div flex-="col gap:1" space-="px:1">
      <h2>Chat Settings</h2>
      
      <div flex-="col gap:1">
        <div flex-="row justify:between">
          <span>Model:</span>
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background1">WebTUI GPT-4</span>
        </div>
        <div flex-="row justify:between">
          <span>Temperature:</span>
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background1">0.7</span>
        </div>
        <div flex-="row justify:between">
          <span>Max Length:</span>
          <span is-="badge" variant-="background1">4096 tokens</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Conversation Stats</h3>
      <div flex-="col gap:1">
        <div flex-="row justify:between">
          <span>Messages:</span>
          <span>4</span>
        </div>
        <div flex-="row justify:between">
          <span>Tokens Used:</span>
          <span>1,245 / 4,096</span>
        </div>
        <div flex-="row justify:between">
          <span>Started:</span>
          <span>10:30 AM</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Available Commands</h3>
      <div flex-="col gap:1">
        <div><code>/clear</code> - Clear conversation</div>
        <div><code>/save</code> - Save conversation</div>
        <div><code>/help</code> - Show help</div>
        <div><code>/model [name]</code> - Change model</div>
      </div>

      <div flex-="row gap:1 wrap">
        <button box-="round" variant-="background1">&#xf2f1; Reset</button>
        <button box-="round" variant-="background1">&#xf0c7; Save</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  #sidebar {
    min-width: 24ch;
    height: 100%;
    --box-border-color: var(--background1);
  }

  #chat-container {
    --box-border-color: var(--background1);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  #info-panel {
    --box-border-color: var(--background1);
  }

  #chat-messages {
    flex-grow: 1;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  #chat-input {
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .message {
    --box-border-color: var(--background2);
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .message.system {
    --box-border-color: var(--background3);
  }

  .message.user {
    --box-border-color: var(--foreground2);
  }

  .message.assistant {
    --box-border-color: var(--foreground1);
  }

  .typing-indicator {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    height: 1lh;
  }

  .dot {
    animation: typing 1.5s infinite;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .dot:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 0.5s;
  }

  .dot:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 1s;
  }

  @keyframes typing {
    0%, 100% {
      opacity: 0.3;
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  pre {
    white-space: pre;
    overflow-x: auto;
    background-color: var(--background1);
    padding: 0.5lh 1ch;
  }
</style>